# Consistent hashing ring: nearest node id for key.
*nearest(nodes as Vec of i64, n as i64, key as i64) returns i64
    best is nodes.get(0)
    i is 1
    while i < n
        if nodes.get(i) >= key and (best < key or nodes.get(i) < best)
            best is nodes.get(i)
        i is i + 1
    best

*main
    nd is vec()
    nd.push(10)
    nd.push(40)
    nd.push(75)
    nd.push(120)
    log nearest(nd, 4, 50)
    log nearest(nd, 4, 80)
